Intended use & safety (not legal advice — confirm for your jurisdiction)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Tepna computes biometric patterns from your wearable and sensor data to support
personal self-quantification. It is NOT a medical device, does not diagnose,
treat, cure, screen for, or prevent any disease or condition, and is not a
substitute for professional clinical evaluation. It has not been reviewed or
cleared by the FDA, CE, or any regulatory body. Always consult a qualified
healthcare provider about your health. Use at your own risk. For research and
personal use only. 100% local: no data leaves your device.

